rows.label: tlk42400013_05_msg0001
rows.name:
To interfere with the summit meeting... Bahn
is quite reckless, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_05_msg0002
rows.name:
He must have been desperate after falling
from his position as Chairman of the Trade Guild, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_05_msg0003
rows.name:
Otherwise, he would never have thought of attacking
a heavily guarded summit meeting, mo.

rows.label: tlk42400013_05_msg0004
rows.name:
If he hadn't been doing bad things from the start,
this wouldn't have happened, mo.
